OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPatchy cloud
OL,6,Fwith further showers for many into the
OL,7,Fevening and overnight. A fresh
OL,8,Fnorthwesterly breeze will continue.
OL,9,FTemperatures falling to low single
OL,10,Ffigures in places but remaining
OL,11,Fgenerally frost free.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAnother day of bright spells
OL,14,Fand occasional heavy showers, these
OL,15,Fcontinuing to bring the risk of some
OL,16,Fhail and thunder. Turning gradually
OL,17,Fdrier through the evening.
OL,18,FTemperatures remaining cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
