OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDrier
OL,6,Finto Friday and Saturday, sunny spells
OL,7,Fbut temperatures a little below
OL,8,Faverage. Likely cloudier Sunday with
OL,9,Fsome rain possible, but temperatures
OL,10,Fturning milder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
